title: DJ Logic - Mystery Mix 15 - Recorded on [2000.03.03]
description:
DJ LOGIC
"MYSTERY MIX 15"

Recorded 03.03.00
Total Running Time 60:16


ropeadope&#039;s own dj logic put together this mystery mix of
old-school funk, hip-hop and totally random shit.

"i was just hanging out in the studio in between sessions 
and i had all my show records with me, i just started 
spinning them for the engineer while we puffed some la, 
watching the springtime clouds roll across the new york 
skyline". 

good thing for us, the engineer in question (rob brand) was 
recording it. listen now. recommended for: cleaning the apartment, 
barbecues in the backyard or a long drive to nowhere.
